cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper presents a neural network-based algorithm for solving high-dimensional stochastic mean field games, which involves optimization and game theory concepts. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
